	<div style="text-align:right;">
		PINEL, Luís Felipe Marinho<sup>1</sup>; SZEJKA, Anderson Luis<sup>2</sup>; TRAPP, Altermir<sup>3</sup>; OKUMURA, Maria Lucia Miyake<sup>4</sup>; CANCIGLIERI JUNIOR, Osiris<sup>5</sup>		<BR>
